Torrent Client
==============

This is a hobby project, which is mainly in C. I'm using this project as a way to learn some advanced linux and C programming.
This torrent client is a program that is built from ground up without using any 3rd party libraries. With the exception of Sockets, OpenSSL for hashing.

Build
=====

./autogen.sh
./configure
make

Testing
=======

make check

